name: Meta X Meta-Architecture _001F
description:
This is the last piece of the 001 collection of the Meta X Meta Architecture series. 

The pre-existing void in the work breaks with the base creating a place of chaos, although the result it produces is harmonious.  We create spatiality from the dis order but that chaos gives us harmony, The towers rise and fall dancing among themselves the song of emptiness, then everything returns to the beginning, the spatiality is reconstructed, peace, stillness, silence... and the cycle begins again.
